### PGNServer Endpoint Tests

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api/v1
# Token akan otomatis diisi jika ekstensi REST Client di VSCode digunakan dan request login dijalankan.
@token = {{login.response.body.data.token}}

### 1. Cek Sistem
GET {{baseUrl}}/cek_sistem

### 2. Registrasi Pengguna
# @name register
POST {{baseUrl}}/otentikasi/daftar
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "nama_lengkap": "Leader QC",
    "nip": "2211019",
    "kata_sandi": "admin"
}

### 3. Login Pengguna
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/otentikasi/masuk
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "nip": "2211019",
    "kata_sandi": "admin"
}

### 4. Lupa Sandi
POST {{baseUrl}}/otentikasi/lupa-sandi
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "nip": "2211019"
}

### 4.5 Logout Pengguna (Memerlukan JWT)
POST {{baseUrl}}/otentikasi/keluar
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. Rekam Lembar Periksa (Memerlukan JWT)
POST {{baseUrl}}/operasi/rekam_lembar_periksa
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "tanggal": "2026-05-17T00:00:00Z",
    "zona_lini": "Lini 1",
    "pengguna_id_tercatat": 1,
    "rincian_inspeksi": [
        {
            "unik_material_bom_id": 1,
            "jam_periksa": "08:00",
            "total_produksi": 100,
            "kuantitas_ok": 98,
            "kuantitas_ng": 2,
            "kode_cacat": "A",
            "catatan": "Material cacat bentuk"
        }
    ]
}

### 5.5 Riwayat Lembar Periksa (Memerlukan JWT)
GET {{baseUrl}}/operasi/riwayat_lembar_periksa?limit=5&offset=0
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. Analitik Metrik Pareto Bulanan
GET {{baseUrl}}/analitik/metrik_pareto_bulanan?bulan=5&tahun=2026

### 7. Unggah Media Material (Memerlukan JWT)
POST {{baseUrl}}/materials/1/media
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="berkas"; filename="sample.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./sample.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### 8. Pratinjau Media
GET {{baseUrl}}/media/1/pratinjau

### 9. Analitik Pareto Dinamis
GET {{baseUrl}}/analitik/pareto?start_date=2026-05-17&end_date=2026-05-17&line=Lini 1

### 10. Analitik Pelacakan Akar Masalah (BOM Tracing)
GET {{baseUrl}}/analitik/lacak?kode_cacat=LAMINATING BOLONG&parent_sku=FG-002

### 11. Simulasi CORS Preflight Request (OPTIONS)
OPTIONS http://localhost:8080/api/v1/cek_sistem
Origin: http://localhost:3000
Access-Control-Request-Method: GET
Access-Control-Request-Headers: Content-Type, Authorization

### 12. Simulasi Secure Enterprise Headers Check
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/cek_sistem

### 13. Simulasi IP Whitelist - Akses Lolos (Menggunakan IP Tepercaya 127.0.0.1)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/krusial/status
X-Forwarded-For: 127.0.0.1

### 14. Simulasi IP Whitelist - Akses Ditolak (Menggunakan IP Asing)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/krusial/status
X-Forwarded-For: 192.168.1.99
